# ── Local-first mode ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# No environment variables required. Drop graph.json in the browser and go.

# ── Optional: hosted persistence (Supabase — deferred scope) ─────────────────
# Uncomment and fill these in only if you deploy the hosted multi-user mode.
# See README §"Hosted persistence (deferred)" for the schema.

# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://xxxx.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...

# ── Optional: Google OAuth (required only alongside Supabase) ─────────────────
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=xxxx.apps.googleusercontent.com
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=GOCSPX-...
# NEXTAUTH_SECRET=<random 32-char string>
# NEXTAUTH_URL=https://your-vercel-deployment.vercel.app
